\f3\fs20 The Republican Legislature led by Gov. Nathan Deal in Georgia is showing the world how fat and selfish we're becoming in this country. Our forefathers who dealt with British spies and countless other challenges would look aghast at how we are becoming. We see refugees, including women and children, fighting to stay alive, and we are frightened of helping them because we fear dying.
